{
  "chapter": 38,
  "chapter_summary": "第三回《缺了半边的人》讲述陆小凤在天福客栈遭遇三拨人跟踪：春水般温柔的丁香姨、五个骑马佩刀的汉子、以及伪装成老学究的西方魔教岁寒三友。陆小凤与丁香姨发生关系后，发现跟踪他的五人已被岁寒三友杀害。丁香姨透露她是方玉香（蓝胡子之妻）的表姐，受托照顾陆小凤。次日又有七人跟踪，其中\"阴童子\"（原名阴阳童子，被司空摘星毁去一半）最为可怕。陆小凤收到装有人牙和黑带子的木箱，意识到黑带组织的威胁，决定主动出击寻找阴童子。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_hu_zi",
      "speaker_name": "蓝胡子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这世上假如有一个人能替你们找回罗刹牌，这个人就是陆小凤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是想替我找个女人来陪我睡觉？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女人我当然想要的，只不过也得看是什么样的女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_xiao_er",
      "speaker_name": "店小二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别的女人我不敢说，可是这个女人，我保证客官一定满意，因为……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道还是她要你来找我的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位是丁姑娘，丁香姨，这位是陆公子，你们两位多亲近亲近！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她微笑着，用一双天真无邪的眼睛直视着他，",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也不是来陪你捉迷藏的！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看得出！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看得出你已是个大男人，我知道你一定也不喜欢捉迷藏！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也没有病？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一点病都没有！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好我没有自作多情，也没有自我陶醉！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是给我的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "全都给你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道这世上有种最古老的赚钱法子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "用这种法子赚钱的女人，通常都叫做婊子！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "用这种法子赚钱的男人，就叫做吃软饭的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就知道你是个聪明人，一点就透！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这五万两银子，并不是我给你的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我表姐！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你表姐是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我表姐就是蓝胡子的老婆、方玉飞的妹妹！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她还有个名字，叫香香！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她知道你出手一向大方，生怕你路上没钱花，又怕你晚上睡不着，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以她就要我来陪你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对我怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们好像从昨天晚上就开始盯上你了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知不知道他们是什么人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怕！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怕什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "后来那七个人里，有个'缺了半边'的，样子长得好凶！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最可怕的，还是他没有缺的那半边！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "布娃娃？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他年纪并不大，个子也很小，一张脸本来一定是圆圆的娃娃脸，可是现在……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你认得他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "改什么名字？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阴童子！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "司空摘星为什么不索性杀了他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为司空摘星一向很少杀人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也有件事想不通！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么从来也不会脸红呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "店小二送来的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁叫他送来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "箱子里有什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只怕里面会钻出个女人来，像你一样的女人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这五根黑带子又是什么意思？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只知道一件事！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "男人的事，女人最好不要多管，也不要多问！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你应该知道，至少我们已不是陌生人！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你就该替我去做一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但是我一定要让他们知道这件事！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "箱子已送过去了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们说了些什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么都没有说！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "书僮也不知道他们在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他绝不会找来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xiang_yi",
      "speaker_name": "丁香姨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
